| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4586 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2d895d09-d16a-500a-9552-863bb6717235"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
